  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK946">
<l>iḻivaṟin tuṇpāṉka ṇiṉpampō ṉiṟkuṅ </l>
<l>kaḻipē riraiyāṉka ṇōy</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As pleasure dwells with him who eats moderately, so disease (dwells) with the glutton who eats voraciously.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
